
Of Good Report ni filime y’urukundo yo muri Afurika y'epfo yakinwe 2013, iyobowe na Jahmil XT Qubeka . Filime yari ifite Mothusi Magano na Petronella Tshuma mu nshingano zabo. Mu bihembo bya 10 bya Afurika Movie Academy Awards, yari bifite ibihembo byinshi , kandi yegukana igihembo cya Afurika Movie Academy Academy cya Filime Nziza .  Iyi filime yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Toronto 2013. 

Muri Nyakanga 2013, mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya 34 rya Durban, filime yatoranijwe mbere yo gufungura iri serukiramuco yatangaje ko yabujijwe na Fondasiyo y’igihugu ya Filime na Video kubera ko irimo "porunogarafiya y’abana", iki cyemezo cyaje gukurwaho nyuma y’ubujurire n'abatunganya firime. 

